Required Python Modules:
-----------------------------------------------------------
- python-reportlab (>= 2.5)
http://pypi.python.org/pypi/reportlab

- python-qrencode (>= 1.0)
http://pypi.python.org/pypi/qrencode

- python-gnupg (>= 0.2.7)
http://pypi.python.org/pypi/python-gnupg

- gnupg executable


Debian testing:
-----------------------------------------------------------
aptitude install python-reportlab python-qrencode gnupg

Install python-gnupg:
1. Download newest tar.gz from http://code.google.com/p/python-gnupg/downloads/list
2. Install package following supplied README